{"tid":2051371,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[塔羅占卜] 有心事嘅同我入嚟 擺底你嘅問題俾我開解你","createTime":"2020-06-04T17:24:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T16:18:42.000Z","uid":342290,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e7dd96ed2322295e2f86bcd30d2d9ce3df2adad4","tid":2051371,"uid":342290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T17:24:42.000Z","msg":"呢一年嚟我諗大家都經歷過好多辛酸史<br />\n內心又有好多感受都&ldquo;有口說不得&rdquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就下定決心學塔羅占卜去做療癒<br />\n希望可以開解到人唔好再咁負<br />\n學完幫唔同朋友試過佢地都覺得舒服咗好多<br />\n所以就想再去幫多啲其他人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果你有唔開心或者煩惱想問吓有咩建議<br />\n又唔介意我用錄音轟炸你嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n歡迎你去tg搵我<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/freetarotguru\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ffreetarotguru&d=OUx24mKaoEPTVTG9WcU5EpmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=1b184e84\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/freetarotguru</a> <br />\n就算解完牌你覺得仲有心事想傾<br />\n我都會繼續陪你傾放心<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 去tg留言&ldquo;免費塔羅占卜&rdquo;<br />\n2. 稱呼(中/英文名 唔好係簡寫)同性別<br />\n3. 精簡嘅背景(例如: 同對象目前嘅關係)<br />\n4. 問題(只限2020年內嘅事同避免時間性問題)<br />\n<br />\n我未必可以即時覆到你因為都要排隊等<br />\n但保證一定一個不漏唔會扮睇你唔到<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">不過 請注意!!!</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n塔羅永遠都唔係model answer!!!<br />\n唔好張牌咁講你就覺得一定係要咁做<br />\n佢只係喺你迷惘嘅時候提點你一下<br />\n但你嘅人生係點最終都係要由你自己決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">重點: 請互相尊重 保持返應有嘅禮貌</span></span></strong><br />\n如果我解完就del chat或者已讀不回嘅話<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁你可以直接唔洗搵我<br />\n想人幫你都要心存善意交流<br />\n我先可以最大程度開解你俾到最貼切嘅建議你<br />\n有緣嘅話都可以成為朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a586468efadd5fe7662314ff9d31ce8780d2ea3","tid":2051371,"uid":342290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T17:38:34.000Z","msg":"出完po瞓教先 瞓醒再占<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"633a1fb61ce8f7a035174c57ea1a3ba26fb5a519","tid":2051371,"uid":342290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T03:56:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f7ae8d8c931c735b2a3fe6347c88fcca2657b91","tid":2051371,"uid":342290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T03:56:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"844ed9a35910c2e6eaf4a111d1b59b56ed6df716","tid":2051371,"uid":342290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T03:56:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e7318d36bb0101c260ec8949d1c0b625638904a","tid":2051371,"uid":342290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T06:53:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a9c535ea5fbe241108474ffa8f787dc19f5c823","tid":2051371,"uid":245556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T08:18:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31cc5ce532f56996cf618abcd75a09f972148752","tid":2051371,"uid":310107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T08:39:16.000Z","msg":"tg咗喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f3bd413d1860d4b19b5f4bcf41266ba176d5ea7","tid":2051371,"uid":245556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTi